an]] (Uzbekistan)\n|149 / 150\n|[[Russian Railways]]\n|3738\n|33\n|Bi-Weekly\n|72 hours (~3 days)\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tutu.travel/poezda/view_d.php?np=ce3e10|title=Tutu travel- Moscow to Andizhan (Andijan)|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|-\n| 39\n| [[Jinan]] (China)\n| [[Urumqi]] (China)\n| Z105/6\n| [[China Railway]]\n| 3726\n| 25\n| Daily\n| 37 hrs 32 mins (~1.5 days)\n|<ref name=\"12306.cn\" />\n|-\n|40\n|[[Moscow]] (Russia)\n|[[Bishkek]] (Kyrgyzstan)\n|017 / 018\n|[[Russian Railways]]\n|3720\n|37\n|Bi-weekly\n|72 hours (~3 days) \n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tutu.travel/poezda/view_d.php?np=e25b2185|title=Tutu travel Moscow \u2013 Bishkek|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|-\n| 41\n| [[Lianyungang]] (China)\n| [[Urumqi]] (China)\n| K1354/3\n| [[China Railway]]\n| 3699\n| 29\n| Daily\n| 47 hrs 05 mins (~2 days)\n|<ref name=\"12306.cn\" />\n|-\n| 42\n|[[Mangalore|Mangalore (India)]]\n| [[Jammu]] (India)\n| [[Navyug Express]]/16687\n| [[Indian Railways]]\n| 3674\n| 71\n| Weekly\n| 68 hrs 5 mins (~3 days)\n|\n|-\n| 43\n| [[Chicago Union Station|Chicago]] (United States)\n| [[Union Station (Los Angeles)|Los Angeles]] (United States)\n| [[Southwest Chief]] 3 / 4\n| [[Amtrak]]\n| 3645\n| 31\n| Daily\n| 41 hrs (~2 days)\n|<ref name=\"amtrak.com \u2013 Southwest Chief\">{{cite web|url=http://www.amtrak.com/southwest-chief-train|title=Southwest Chief|date=|author=|work=amtrak.com|accessdate=2 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 44\n| [[Chicago Union Station|Chicago]] (United States)\n| [[Portland, Oregon|Portland]] (United States)\n| [[Empire Builder]] 27 / 28\n| [[Amtrak]]\n| 3629\n| 38\n| Daily\n| 46 hrs (~2 days)\n|<ref name=\"amtrak.com \u2013 Empire Builder\">{{cite web|url=http://www.amtrak.com/empire-builder-train|title=Empire Builder|date=|author=|work=amtrak.com|accessdate=2 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 45\n| [[Tirunelveli]] (India)\n| [[Jammu]] (India)\n| Tirunelveli-Jammu Express/16787\n| [[Ind