oscow]] \n| [[Vladivostok]]\n| 100E/099E\n| [[Russian Railways]]\n| 10317&nbsp;km\n| 103\n| Daily\n| 166 hrs(~7 days)\n|}\n\n==== South Korea ====\n<!--- Please add \"Operator\" column only if there different operators. --->\nAll services are operated by [[Korail]].\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Cheongnyangni Station|Cheongnyangni]] \n| [[Bujeon Station (Korail)|Bujeon]]\n| 1621\u20131624\n| 483.1&nbsp;km\n| 18/31\n| Twice daily\n| 7 ~ 8 hrs\n|-\n| [[Jeongdongjin Station|Jeongdongjin]] ([[Gangneung Station|Gangneung]]) \n| [[Busan Station|Busan]]\n| 1691/1692\n| 480.5&nbsp;km\n| \n| Daily\n| 7.9 hrs\n|-\n| [[Jeongdongjin Station|Jeongdngjin]] ([[Gangneung Station|Gangneung]]) \n| [[Bujeon Station (Korail)|Bujeon]]\n| 1681/1682\n| 453.5&nbsp;km\n| \n| Daily\n| 7.9 hrs\n|-\n| [[Bujeon Station (Korail)|Bujeon]] \n| [[Mokpo Station|Mokpo]] via [[Seogwangju Station|Seogwangju]]\n| 1951/1954\n| 390.9&nbsp;km\n| 46\n| Daily\n| 6.5 hrs\n|-\n| [[Dongdaegu Station|Dongdaegu]] \n| [[Yeongju Station|Yeongju]] via [[Daejeon Station|Daejeon]]\n| 4301\u20134304\n| 387.5&nbsp;km\n| 22\n| Twice daily\n| 5.25 hrs\n|}\n\n==== Taiwan ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Taipei]] \n| [[Hualien City|Hualien]]\n| 51/52\n| [[Taiwan Railways Administration]]\n| 752&nbsp;km\n| 17\n| daily\n| 10 hours 30 mins\n|-\n|}\n\n==== Thailand ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Bangkok]] \n| [[Singapore]]\n| 951/952\n| Locomotive : [[State Railway of Thailand|SRT]] & [[Keretapi Tanah