it of Queensland]]\n| [[Queensland Rail]]\n| 1680&nbsp;km\n| N/A\n| 5 times per week\n| 31 hrs\n|-\n|[[Roma Street railway station|Brisbane]]\n|[[Townsville railway station|Townsville]]\n|[[Spirit of the Outback]]\n|[[Queensland Rail]]\n|1325&nbsp;km\n|25\n|2 times per week\n|26 hrs\n|-\n|[[Central railway station, Sydney|Sydney]]\n|[[Broken Hill railway station|Broken Hill]]\n|[[Outback Xplorer]]\n|[[NSW TrainLink]]\n|1135&nbsp;km\n|16\n|Weekly\n|13 hrs\n|-\n|[[Central railway station, Sydney|Sydney]]\n|[[Roma Street railway station|Brisbane]]\n|NT31 / 32\n|[[NSW TrainLink]]\n|988&nbsp;km\n|22\n|Daily\n|14 hrs 12 min\n|-\n|[[Townsville railway station|Townsville]]\n|[[Mount Isa]]\n|[[The Inlander (Queensland Rail)|The Inlander]]\n|[[Queensland Rail]]\n|977&nbsp;km\n|9\n|2 times per week\n|21 hrs\n|-\n|[[Central railway station, Sydney|Sydney]]\n|[[Southern Cross railway station|Melbourne]]\n|ST21 / 22 / 23 / 24\n|[[NSW TrainLink]]\n|960&nbsp;km\n|16\n|Twice daily each way\n|10 hrs 50 min\n|-\n|[[Adelaide Parklands Terminal|Adelaide]]\n|[[Southern Cross railway station|Melbourne]]\n|[[The Overland]]\n|[[Journey Beyond]]\n|828&nbsp;km\n|9\n|2 times per week\n|10 hrs 30 min\n|}\n\n==== New Zealand ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width= align=\n|+ \n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Auckland]]\n| [[Wellington]]\n| [[Northern Explorer]] 200 / 201\n| [[KiwiRail Scenic Journeys]]\n| 682&nbsp;km\n| 7\n| 3 times per week \n| 11 hrs\n|}\n\n== Longest non-stop train services, by distance & country ==\n<!-- To keep it nice to read and the table compact, please add only one entry per country -->\n\n=== Asia ===\n==== China ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width= align=\n|+ \n! No\n! Origin City(Country)\n! Destination City(Country) \n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! Frequency\n! Running Time\n! Average Speed\n! {{abbr