rains operating nationally, within a country.\n\n=== Africa ===\n\n==== Egypt ====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Alexandria]] \n| [[Aswan]] \n| No. 88 Special (\"Isbani\")\n| [[Egyptian National Railways]]\n| 1100&nbsp;km (approximate)\n| 9\n| Daily\n| 17 hrs\n|}\n\n==== South Africa ====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Pretoria]] \n| [[Cape Town]] \n| [[Blue Train (South Africa)|The Blue Train]]\n| Luxrail\n| 1&nbsp;600&nbsp;km\n| 7\n| weekly\n| 28 hrs\n|}\n\n=== Asia ===\n\n==== China ====\nAll services are operated by [[China Railway]].\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Guangzhou railway station|Guangzhou]] \n| [[Lhasa railway station|Lhasa]]\n| Z264 / Z266\n| 4980&nbsp;km\n| 10\n| 54 h (2 days +)\n|-\n| [[Qiqihar railway station|Qiqihar]] \n| [[\u00dcr\u00fcmqi railway station|\u00dcr\u00fcmqi]]\n| K1084 / K1081\n| 4827 km\n| 40\n| 62 h 15 min<ref>https://kyfw.12306.cn</ref>(2 days +)\n|-\n| [[Yining]] \n| [[Shanghai railway station|Shanghai]]\n| T206 / T203\n| 4742&nbsp;km\n| 32\n| 54 h (2 days +)\n|-\n| [[Shenzhen railway station|Shenzhen]] \n| [[\u00dcr\u00fcmqi railway station|Urumqi]]\n| Z230 / Z231\n| 4657&nbsp;km\n| 20\n| 48 h 17 mins (2 days +)\n|-\n| [[Shanghai railway station|Shanghai]] \n| [[Lhasa railway station|Lhasa]]\n| Z164 / Z166\n| 4373&nbsp;km\n| 12\n| 48 h (2 days)\n|-\n| [[Harbin]]\n| [[Haikou]]\n| Z114 / Z112\n| 4276&nbsp;km\n| 29\n| 46 hrs 54 mins (~2 days)\n|-\n| [[Kunming]]\n| [[\u00dcr\u00fcmqi railway station|Urumqi]]\n| K1502 / 