ory.\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width= align=\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Vorkuta]] \n| [[Adler Microdistrict|Adler]] \n| 309\n| [[Russian Railways]]\n| 4286&nbsp;km\n| 78\n| once in two days\n| 89 hrs\n|-\n| [[Murmansk]] \n| [[Moscow]]\n| 015\n| [[Russian Railways|RZD]]\n| 2100&nbsp;km\n| 31\n| daily\n| 35 hrs\n|}\n\n==== Spain ====\nAll services operated by [[Renfe]]\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width= align=\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[Barcelona]] \n| [[Vigo]]\n| Trenhotel\n00921/00922\n| approx. 1300&nbsp;km\n| 21\n| daily\n| 14 hrs, 54 mins (00921)\n15 hrs, 20 mins (00922)\n|-\n| [[Barcelona]] \n| [[A Coru\u00f1a]]\n| Trenhotel\n00921/00922\n| approx. 1200&nbsp;km\n| 21\n| daily\n| 15 hrs (00921)\n14 hrs, 55 mins (00922)\n|-\n| [[Barcelona]] \n| [[A Coru\u00f1a]]\n| Alvia\n00625/00626\n| approx. 1100&nbsp;km\n| 24\n| 4 times a week\n| 13 hrs, 20 mins (00625)\n13 hrs (00626)\n|}\n\n==== Sweden ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width= align=\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[G\u00f6teborg]] \n| [[Lule\u00e5]]\n| 91\n| [[SJ AB|SJ]]\n| 1400&nbsp;km\n| 16\n| daily\n| 17 hrs, 27 mins\n|}\n\n==== Switzerland ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width= align=\n|+ \n|-\n! Origin City\n! Destination City\n! Train Name/No\n! Operator Name \n! Distance\n! No.of Stops\n! Frequency\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Scheduled running time\n|-\n| [[St. Gallen railway station|St Gallen]] \n| [[Geneva Airport railway station|Geneva Airport]]\n| IC1\n| [[Swiss Federal Railways|SBB&nbsp;CFF&nbsp;CFF]]\n| approx. 350&nbsp;km\n| 9\n| hourly\n| 4 hrs